✓ Auditor View (Tab 2)
  - Large risk score header with color-coded background
    * Green (>80%), Yellow (50-80%), Red (<50%)
  - Draft input textarea
  - Color-coded sentence analysis
    * VERIFIED: Green background with CheckCircle icon
    * UNKNOWN: Yellow background with AlertTriangle icon
    * CONTRADICTION: Red background with XCircle icon
  - Detailed explanations and vault references
  - Summary section
  - Empty state when no analysis exists

✓ Vault View (Tab 3)
  - Large textarea editor (20+ rows) for knowledge base content
  - "Save & Index" primary button
  - "Load Sample Data" secondary button with enterprise security policy
  - Info box explaining vault purpose
  - Success feedback messages (no toast notifications)
  - Browser-based state management

